---
---
<section class="bg-white py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-8 md:px-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3">

            <!-- Marca -->
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 py-12 md:py-0 md:pr-12 border-l-2 border-black pl-8 md:pl-10">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-medium tracking-wide">— Identidad</p>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black leading-none tracking-tight">Marca</h2>
                <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 list-none p-0">
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">
                        Desarrollamos el universo conceptual y creamos la identidad de la marca: nombre, diseño, aplicación y manuales de uso.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <ul class="mt-auto flex flex-wrap gap-2 list-none p-0">
                    <li class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/15 text-black/50">Naming</li>
                    <li class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/15 text-black/50">Identidad visual</li>
                    <li class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/15 text-black/50">Diseño</li>
                    <li class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/15 text-black/50">Manual de marca</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Comunicación y Contenido -->
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 py-12 md:py-0 md:px-12 border-l-2 border-black pl-8 md:pl-10 mt-12 md:mt-0">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-medium tracking-wide">— Estrategia</p>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black leading-none tracking-tight">Comunicación<br/>y Contenido</h2>
                <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 list-none p-0">
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Diseñamos y gestionamos planes de comunicación integral: diagnóstico, estrategia, creatividad y manual de comunicación.</li>
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Administramos e implementamos la comunicación en plataformas digitales y medios tradicionales.</li>
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Implementamos campañas 360°.</li>
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Desarrollamos sitios web sostenibles.</li>
                </ul>
                <ul class="mt-auto flex flex-wrap gap-2 list-none p-0">
                    <li class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/15 text-black/50">Planes de comunicación</li>
                    <li class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/15 text-black/50">Redes sociales</li>
                    <li class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/15 text-black/50">Campañas 360°</li>
                    <li class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/15 text-black/50">Sitios web</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Consultoría -->
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 py-12 md:py-0 border-l-2 border-black pl-8 md:pl-12 mt-12 md:mt-0">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-medium tracking-wide">— Impacto</p>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black leading-none tracking-tight">Consultoría</h2>
                <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 list-none p-0">
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Identificamos y desarrollamos planes y modelos de negocio.</li>
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Elaboramos diagnósticos de triple impacto (social, ambiental y económico) para productos, proyectos y empresas.</li>
                    <li class="relative pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.55em] before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-black/20">Diseñamos e implementamos estrategias de impacto positivo.</li>
                </ul>
                <ul class="mt-auto flex flex-wrap gap-2 list-none p-0">
                    <li class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/15 text-black/50">Modelos de negocio</li>
                    <li class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/15 text-black/50">Triple impacto</li>
                    <li class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/15 text-black/50">Impacto positivo</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
